\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Jersey City has rapidly evolved into a premier urban destination for dog owners, seamlessly blending high-density living with accessible green spaces along the Hudson River waterfront. The city’s commitment to canine enrichment is evident in meticulously maintained facilities like the Hamilton Park Dog Run and the expansive \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://nj.gov/dep/parksandforests/parks/libertystatepark.html\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Lincoln Park\\\"}],null,\\\" in nearby \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/states/new-jersey\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"New Jersey\\\"}],null,\\\", which offers separate zones for large and small breeds to ensure safe socialization. For residents of high-rise developments in Newport or Exchange Place, the availability of artificial turf runs and well-lit evening spaces provides a critical outlet for energy and socialization in a climate-controlled urban environment. The local community is highly active, often organizing meetups and advocating for pet-friendly policies that keep Jersey City at the forefront of metropolitan pet culture.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Beyond the designated runs, Jersey City’s walkability makes it ideal for leashed exploration through historic neighborhoods and popular waterfront esplanades. Popular spots like Sgt. Anthony Park and the newer Berry Lane Park demonstrate the city’s proactive approach to urban planning, integrating pet amenities into revitalized industrial zones. Responsible ownership is central to the local experience, with the \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://jerseycitynj.gov/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Jersey City Health Department\\\"}],null,\\\" mandating annual licensing and rabies vaccinations to maintain a healthy public environment. Whether you are seeking a quick morning sprint at Van Vorst Park or a scenic weekend stroll overlooking the Manhattan skyline, our \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"city directory\\\"}],null,\\\" provides real-time updates on amenity availability and local seasonal protocols. By prioritizing both safety and variety, Jersey City ensures that every urban pup remains engaged and healthy regardless of the neighborhood.\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta primary\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"park-directory\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"Browse directory\\\"]}],\\\"$L32\\\",\\\"$L33\\\"]}],\\\"$L34\\\"]}],\\\"$L35\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\",\\\"$L3f\\\",\\\"$L40\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"IndoorDogPark\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\