ordogpark.org/parks/a-bark-away-nj\",\"description\":\"A Bark Away NJ in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) offers a versatile and modern approach to canine care, specializing in balanced training programs that seamlessly integrate into the busy...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/allforthewag\",\"name\":\"Allforthewag\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/allforthewag\",\"description\":\"Allforthewag brings a personalized, boutique approach to dog care in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), operating locations in the popular SOHO West and Bergen-Lafayette neighborhoods. Run by a...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/allforthewag-bergen-lafayette\",\"name\":\"Allforthewag Bergen Lafayette\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/allforthewag-bergen-lafayette\",\"description\":\"Allforthewag Bergen Lafayette in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished, family-operated pet resort that has quickly become a cornerstone of the neighborhood's animal community...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/barky-way\",\"name\":\"BARKY WAY\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/barky-way\",\"description\":\"BARKY WAY in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished, one-on-one pet care boutique that redefines the urban experience by combining master grooming with professional obedience...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/casa-de-boop\",\"name\":\"Casa De Boop\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/casa-de-boop\",\"description\":\"Casa De Boop in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is an elite, high-touch pet care enclave that operates with a signature 'Mi Casa Su Casa' philosophy, providing a deeply restorative and...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":6,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/furever-fresh-dog-grooming-day-care\",\"name\":\"Furever Fresh Dog Grooming + Day Care\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/furever-fresh-dog-grooming-day-care\",\"description\":\"Tucked away in the scenic landscape of [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), Furever Fresh Dog Grooming + Day Care offers a refreshing escape into nature for you and your four-legged companion. This...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/happy-paws\",\"name\":\"Happy Paws\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/happy-paws\",\"description\":\"Happy Paws in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a dedicated pet care hub that prides itself on providing a personalized and deeply affectionate environment for the local canine community....\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pawfessional-pet-care\",\"name\":\"Pawfessional Pet Care\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pawfessional-pet-care\",\"description\":\"If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), look no further than Pawfessional Pet Care. This vibrant community destination has earned a...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/paws-go\",\"name\":\"Paws & Go\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/paws-go\",\"description\":\"Paws & Go in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a premier mobile pet care destination that brings the world-class grooming experience of a high-end salon directly to your home or workplace....\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/paws-for-thought-dog-training-jersey-city\",\"name\":\"Paws for Thought Dog Training Jersey City\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/paws-for-thought-dog-training-jersey-city\",\"description\":\"Paws for Thought Dog Training in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) offers a sophisticated and deeply empathetic approach to canine behavior, specializing in personalized, science-backed solutions...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}25:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2d\"}}]\n2e:T1de3,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How many dog parks are available in Jersey City?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Jersey City has 47 dog parks and dog-friendly establishments, including traditional outdoor dog parks, indoor dog parks, and dog-friendly businesses like restaurants and shops. Each type offers unique benefits for different situations and dog personalities.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any indoor dog parks in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! The United States is home to hundreds of indoor dog parks, and the industry is growing rapidly. IndoorDogPark.org maintains the most comprehensive directory available, currently tracking over 360 verified facilities across 155 cities nationwide. These climate-controlled spaces solve real problems for dog owners. In cities like Phoenix where summer temperatures can exceed 110°F, or Chicago where winter brings sub-zero temperatures for months, indoor parks become essential. They're also invaluable in rainy regions like Seattle or Portland, where outdoor parks stay muddy for much of the year. Our directory includes detailed profiles for each facility: amenities, pricing structures, operating hours, vaccination requirements, and real visitor experiences. We've aggregated over 106,000 user reviews from Google, Yelp, and other platforms to help you make informed decisions. Popular metro areas with the most options include Los Angeles (23 indoor facilities), Chicago (18 facilities), and New York City (15 facilities). But we've also documented smaller markets like Bend, Oregon, and Asheville, North Carolina, where innovative entrepreneurs are meeting local demand. To explore options near you, visit our main directory page or browse by state. Each listing includes photos, direct contact information, and links to facility websites where you can check current availability and make reservations.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dog parks in Jersey City free to use?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most traditional outdoor dog parks in public spaces are free to use. However, indoor dog parks and specialized facilities typically require membership fees or day passes. Dog-friendly establishments like restaurants may have minimum purchase requirements or special pet menus.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the requirements to visit dog parks in Jersey City?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most dog parks require that your dog be current on vaccinations (rabies, DHPP), licensed, and well-behaved. Some indoor facilities may require proof of vaccinations, health certificates, or temperament assessments. Always check specific park rules before visiting.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the best time to visit dog parks in Jersey City?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Early mornings (6–9 AM) and early evenings (4–7 PM) are typically the busiest times, offering great socialization opportunities. Midday visits are usually quieter, better for dogs who may be overwhelmed by crowds. Weekends are generally busier than weekdays. Consider your dog's personality and social comfort level when planning visits.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where to go with a dog when it's raining?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Rainy days don't have to mean canceled playtime. Indoor dog parks are specifically designed for exactly this scenario, offering climate-controlled environments where dogs can exercise and socialize safely. Our directory lists over 360 indoor facilities across the country. Many feature specialized surfaces like K9Grass or rubberized flooring that stay clean and dry regardless of weather. These surfaces are easier on joints than concrete and reduce injury risk compared to muddy outdoor parks. Beyond dedicated indoor parks, consider these alternatives: • Pet stores with play areas: Chains like PetSmart and Petco sometimes host indoor play sessions. • Dog-friendly cafes and restaurants: Many now welcome well-behaved dogs indoors, perfect for socialization in a calmer setting. • Indoor training facilities: Often open their spaces for play sessions between classes. • Doggy daycare centers: Many offer drop-in playtime options for non-members. Pro tip: Indoor facilities get significantly busier during bad weather, so call ahead or book reservations when possible. Many also offer online booking systems for convenience. Bonus: Most indoor parks include dog wash stations, so your pup can get clean before the ride home—no muddy paws in your car. Explore our directory to find indoor options near you, and filter by amenities like \\\"dog wash\\\" or \\\"separate small dog areas\\\" to find exactly what you need.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any size restrictions or separate areas for different sized dogs?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Many dog parks in Jersey City offer separate areas for small dogs (under 25 lbs) and large dogs (over 25 lbs). This helps ensure safe play experiences. However, not all parks have this separation, so it's important to check ahead and supervise your dog's interactions.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What should I bring when visiting a dog park in Jersey City?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Essential items include: a leash (for entering and exiting), poop bags, fresh water and a bowl, your dog's vaccination records (especially for indoor facilities), and your phone for emergencies. Optional items include toys (check park rules first), treats for training, and a first-aid kit.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there indoor dog park options available in Jersey City?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Not yet in our verified directory for Jersey City. If you know a great indoor option, you can submit it and we’ll review it for inclusion.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is the most dog friendly city in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"This question sparks lively debates among dog owners, and the answer depends on what you value most. Based on our analysis of over 360 facilities across 155 cities, here's what the data reveals: California dominates in sheer numbers: Los Angeles, San Diego, and San Francisco collectively host 50+ indoor dog parks. But quantity isn't everything. Cities consistently ranking high for overall dog-friendliness include: • San Francisco: Over 40% of households include dogs (above the 38% national average), extensive off-leash beaches, and one of the highest concentrations of dog parks per capita. • Portland, Oregon: Known for progressive pet policies, abundant green spaces, and a culture where dogs are welcome almost everywhere—including many restaurants and breweries. • Seattle: Over 14 off-leash areas plus multiple indoor facilities, making it ideal for a city that gets 150+ rainy days annually. • Austin, Texas: Boasts some of the largest dog parks in the country, plus a vibrant dog-friendly dining scene. • Denver: High altitude doesn't stop Coloradans—the city maintains excellent park facilities and welcoming policies. However, \\\"friendliness\\\" extends beyond park counts. Factors like pet-friendly rental policies, veterinary care access, breed restrictions, and community culture matter just as much. Our directory lets you explore by city to see specific offerings. Check out our city guides for detailed breakdowns of parks, amenities, and local pet policies. We also maintain guides for major metro areas on our blog, covering everything from best parks to dog-friendly neighborhoods.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Jersey City\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Jersey City\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks in Jersey City, NJ\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Experience vibrant urban play and waterfront trails in the heart of Jersey City.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Jersey City has rapidly evolved into a premier urban destination for dog owners, seamlessly blending high-density living with accessible green spaces along the Hudson River waterfront. The city’s commitment to canine enrichment is evident in meticulously maintained facilities like the Hamilton Park Dog Run and the expansive \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://nj.gov/dep/parksandforests/parks/libertystatepark.html\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Lincoln Park\"}],null,\" in nearby \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/states/new-jersey\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"New Jersey\"}],null,\", which offers separate zones for large and small breeds to ensure safe socialization. For residents of high-rise developments in Newport or Exchange Place, the availability of artificial turf runs and well-lit evening spaces provides a critical outlet for energy and socialization in a climate-controlled urban environment. The local community is highly active, often organizing meetups and advocating for pet-friendly policies that keep Jersey City at the forefront of metropolitan pet culture.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Beyond the designated runs, Jersey City’s walkability makes it ideal for leashed exploration through historic neighborhoods and popular waterfront esplanades. Popular spots like Sgt. Anthony Park and the newer Berry Lane Park demonstrate the city’s proactive approach to urban planning, integrating pet amenities into revitalized industrial zones. Responsible ownership is central to the local experience, with the \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://jerseycitynj.gov/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Jersey City Health Department\"}],null,\" mandating annual licensing and rabies vaccinations to maintain a healthy public environment. Whether you are seeking a quick morning sprint at Van Vorst Park or a scenic weekend stroll overlooking the Manhattan skyline, our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"city directory\"}],null,\" provides real-time updates on amenity availability and local seasonal protocols. By prioritizing both safety and variety, Jersey City ensures that every urban pup remains engaged and healthy regardless of the neighborhood.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[\"$L31\",\"Browse directory\"]}],\"$L32\",\"$L33\"]}],\"$L34\"]}],\"$L35\"]}]}],\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$undefined\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\",\"$L40\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"children\":\"About us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/partners\",\"children\":\"Partners\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Discover\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Browse parks\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/how-it-works\",\"children\":\"How it works\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog\",\"children\":\"Blog\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Park Owners\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"children\":\"List your park\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/owner-resources\",\"children\":\"Owner resources\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Support\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"children\":\"Contact us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/faq\",\"children\":\"FAQ\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Join the Pack\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4 text-sm text-white/70\",\"children\":\"Get the latest indoor dog park news and updates.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"type\":\"consumer\",\"source\":\"footer\",\"variant\":\"dark\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-social\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://x.com/Indoordogp40934\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on X (Twitter)\",\"title\":\"Follow us on X (Twitter)\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-twitter\"}]}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.facebook.com/IndoorDogParkDirectory\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on Facebook\",\"title\":\"Follow us on Facebook\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-facebook\"}]}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.instagram.com/indoordogpark2025/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on Instagram\",\"title\":\"Follow us on Instagram\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-instagram\"}]}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.pinterest.com/indoordogpark/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on Pinterest\",\"title\":\"Follow us on Pinterest\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-pinterest\"}]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://digg.com/indoordogpark\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on Digg\",\"title