I[5535,[\"8500\",\"static/chunks/8500-41fa79ac743d83f1.js\",\"2365\",\"static/chunks/2365-7389548ffb58ad16.js\",\"5772\",\"static/chunks/5772-c985b8ef30d7cbb9.js\",\"615\",\"static/chunks/615-be2f2421adf86c1e.js\",\"7206\",\"static/chunks/7206-a2d01a15ee8aa63c.js\",\"6107\",\"static/chunks/6107-dcaf73e9eac71186.js\",\"4561\",\"static/chunks/4561-fcca530cf2bd8bc5.js\",\"804\",\"static/chunks/app/cities/%5Bslug%5D/page-ad2ba860a46ca666.js\"],\"default\"]\n77:I[8622,[\"8500\",\"static/chunks/8500-41fa79ac743d83f1.js\",\"2365\",\"static/chunks/2365-7389548ffb58ad16.js\",\"5772\",\"static/chunks/5772-c985b8ef30d7cbb9.js\",\"615\",\"static/chunks/615-be2f2421adf86c1e.js\",\"7206\",\"static/chunks/7206-a2d01a15ee8aa63c.js\",\"6107\",\"static/chunks/6107-dcaf73e9eac71186.js\",\"4561\",\"static/chunks/4561-fcca530cf2bd8bc5.js\",\"804\",\"static/chunks/app/cities/%5Bslug%5D/page-ad2ba860a46ca666.js\"],\"default\"]\n78:I[4561,[\"8500\",\"static/chunks/8500-41fa79ac743d83f1.js\",\"2365\",\"static/chunks/2365-7389548ffb58ad16.js\",\"5772\",\"static/chunks/5772-c985b8ef30d7cbb9.js\",\"615\",\"static/chunks/615-be2f2421adf86c1e.js\",\"7206\",\"static/chunks/7206-a2d01a15ee8aa63c.js\",\"6107\",\"static/chunks/6107-dcaf73e9eac71186.js\",\"4561\",\"static/chunks/4561-fcca530cf2bd8bc5.js\",\"804\",\"static/chunks/app/cities/%5Bslug%5D/page-ad2ba860a46ca666.js\"],\"default\"]\n31:[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}]\n32:[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L44\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/jersey-city/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Jersey City dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n36:[\"$\",\"$L45\",null,{\"city\":\"Jersey City\",\"state\":\"NJ\"}]\n47:T733,108 First Street Dog Park in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a sleek and exceptionally well-maintained urban run that provides a high-standard play environment for the downtown canine community. Located prominently at 108 First Street, this fully fenced off-leash park is renowned for its professional-grade AstroTurf surface, which ensures a clean and mud-free experience for both dogs and their owners. The facility is intelligently divided into two distinct sections to separate energetic larger breeds from smaller socialites weighing 25 pounds or less, fostering a safe and controlled atmosphere for all temperaments. The park's signature downtown location, paired with its scrupulous maintenance schedule, makes it a verified local favorite for residents seeking a quick and restorative social break for their companions.\n\nThe amenities at 108 First Street are designed for daily convenience and safety, featuring a dedicated water spout to ensure every pup stays hydrated throughout their stay. Owners can enjoy comfortable, built-in benches that offer a clear line of sight on the play areas, while conveniently located waste disposal stations and trash bins make maintaining the park's high standards an effortless task. The facility can comfortably accommodate approximately a dozen dogs at capacity, creating a vibrant but manageable social hub where neighborhood pets can engage in spirited play. Because of its secure fencing and high-transparency layout, the park provides a sense of security and professional oversight that is highly valued by local pet parents. Whether your pup is an urban athlete looking for a game of keep-away on the turf or a smaller dog in need of gentle social proofing, this First Street landmark treats every guest with the expert logic and modern convenience the downtown community deserves.48:T83a,A Bark Away NJ in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) offers a versatile and modern approach to canine care, specializing in balanced training programs that seamlessly integrate into the busy lifestyle of urban pet parents. Founded by certified trainer Criselda Quan, this service provides a wide range of options from foundational puppy training to advanced behavior modification. Their philosophy is rooted in a structured and compassionate methodology, aiming to build a common language of trust between dogs and their owners. One of their most unique offerings is the 'Bark Pack Walk,' a three-hour social and educational experience that includes complimentary pick-up and drop-off. These supervised group sessions are designed to provide both physical exercise and mental stimulation, allowing dogs to practice polite leash behavior and social impulse control in a real-world park setting under the guidance of a professional trainer.\n\nFor owners seeking more intensive support, A Bark Away NJ provides immersive 'Board & Train' programs for three to five weeks, focusing on deep-seated behavioral issues and elite-level obedience. They also offer a flexible 'Drop-Off Training' service for busy weekdays, where dogs work on focus and manners at the trainer's location before returning home in the evening. For those who prefer to be directly involved, their 'Bark Home School' and private in-home sessions offer personalized coaching in the dog's own environment, addressing everything from potty training to separation anxiety. The service also includes loving and reliable pet sitting, providing a specialized 'Meet and Greet' to ensure every guest is comfortable before an overnight stay. With a commitment to clear communication and long-term results, A Bark Away NJ delivers a verified, high-touch training solution that transforms the way humans and dogs live together in the Jersey City community. Whether you are looking for a routine of spirited pack walks or seeking a total behavioral overhaul, Criselda's expert team treats every dog with the individualized logic and love they deserve.49:T793,Allforthewag Bergen Lafayette in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished, family-operated pet resort that has quickly become a cornerstone of the neighborhood's animal community since its founding by a passionate husband-and-wife team. Located on Communipaw Avenue, this meticulously organized facility features expansive indoor and outdoor play areas designed to offer a vibrant and safe 'PlayCare' experience for dogs of all temperaments. The facility's hallmark is its rigorous screening process, where every guest undergoes a behavioral assessment to ensure they are appropriately paired for social play based on size, breed, and play style. This commitment to 'safe socialization' creates a controlled and harmonious environment that fosters healthy physical exercise and mental development for every pup guest.\n\nThe service menu at Allforthewag is focused on providing high-touch, individualized care through their flagship daycare and 'SleepOver' boarding programs. Owners receive daily photo updates and detailed reports of their pet's activities, ensuring a level of transparency that is highly valued by the local community. The boarding experience is designed to be a stress-free transition from home, providing dogs with familiar routines, secure sleeping quarters, and round-the-clock professional oversight. Because of its verified reputation for cleanliness and the genuine personal connection the owners build with their guests, the facility often maintains a waitlist for new enrollments. The business also features client-centric amenities like loyalty programs and seasonal bundled deals, reinforcing its status as an authoritative and deeply affectionate local resource. Whether your pup is joining for a day of spirited social proofing or an extended boarding stay, the team at Allforthewag treats every guest with the same expert logic and individualized heart they would their own family companions.4a:T7ce,Anything's Pawsible has been a cornerstone of the [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) and Bayonne pet care communities since 2013, offering a level of dedicated service that feels both professional and deeply personal. This family-oriented business specializes in high-quality dog walking and pet sitting, providing a reliable alternative for owners who prefer their pets to stay in the comfort of their own homes. Their signature service includes GPS-verified walks through 'PetCheck' technology, which sends real-time alerts and photos to owners the moment a walk begins and ends. With a team of certified walkers who are both insured and bonded, Anything's Pawsible prioritizes safety and transparency above all else. They take the time to craft customized care plans for every pet, addressing specific feeding schedules, preferred walk routes, and even behavioral conditioning techniques to ensure that every visit is enrichment-filled and consistent with the dog's training goals.\n\nBeyond their daily walking routes, Anything's Pawsible offers comprehensive vacation care, including overnight stays in the client's home or boarding at a staff member's residence, complete with coordinated transportation for added convenience. The service is truly all-inclusive, extending its care to cats and exotic pets, and even handling minor household tasks like watering plants or collecting mail to give travelers total peace of mind. Their 24/7/365 availability means that whether it's a routine workday or a major holiday, Jersey City pet parents can rely on a consistent, caring presence for their animals. With over a decade of experience and thousands of successful visits under their belt, they have built a reputation for 'world-class service' that treats every pet with the love and respect they deserve. Whether you need a quick 20-minute bathroom break for a puppy or a week of dedicated overnight care, Anything's Pawsible delivers a verified, high-touch solution for the modern pet owner.4b:T7a6,BARKY WAY in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished, one-on-one pet care boutique that redefines the urban experience by combining master grooming with professional obedience training. Located prominently on Newark Avenue, this world-class facility is led by Monika Bozyk, an expert trainer and groomer who prioritizes the building of a strong foundation for good behavior in every guest. The salon is celebrated for its 'Safe and Personal' philosophy, where traditional assembly-line grooming is replaced with individualized, distraction-free sessions that are particularly beneficial for senior pets and those with social sensitivities. Its modern, welcoming layout also features a curated retail selection of healthy, natural food products and accessories, ensuring a holistic approach to pet wellness.\n\nThe service menu at BARKY WAY is comprehensive and technically focused, offering everything from basic hygienic maintenance to full-service aesthetic transformations. Their flagship grooming packages include technical de-shedding, coat conditioning, and specialized medicated baths for pets with skin sensitivities, while their training programs focus on building focus and physical agility through positive reinforcement. Safety is paramount at this location, with every appointment scrupulously scheduled to ensure the groomer's undivided attention and a quiet, restorative atmosphere. The facility's recent official recognition and its perfect 5.0-star reputation reflect its status as an authoritative and deeply trusted community resource. Because of its high demand and commitment to one-on-one care, sessions are available by appointment only, ensuring a level of professional reliability that is second to none. Whether your pup is seeking a quiet morning grooming session or foundational obedience support, BARKY WAY treats every guest with the expert logic and personalized heart that defines Monika's professional mission.4c:T7e9,Bergen Bark & Bath in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished, women-owned pet center that uniquely combines a world-class grooming salon with a premier health-focused retail destination. Located prominently on Bergen Avenue, this facility is celebrated for its inclusive and welcoming atmosphere, where every pet family is treated with the same expert logic and care. The salon's hallmark is its holistic approach to animal wellness, where every grooming session includes a professional 'health monitor' assessment to provide early detection of skin issues or other physical concerns. The facility is meticulously organized and features a team of master groomers who provide technical breed-specific styling and therapeutic hygiene treatments tailored to the pet's unique coat type and skin sensitivity.\n\nThe service menu at Bergen Bark & Bath is comprehensive and focuses on both aesthetic beauty and long-term health, featuring deep-cleansing baths with premium organic shampoos, precision nail care, and professional dental hygiene. Beyond the salon, the center serves as an authoritative local resource for high-quality pet supplies, offering a curated selection of natural food products, specialized habitat solutions, and interactive mental enrichment toys. Owners benefit from the staff's expert guidance on product selection and best practices for daily care, as well as unique high-touch amenities like local loyalty programs and seasonal bundled deals. The center is scrupulously maintained and climate-controlled, ensuring a hygienic and comfortable environment for both shopping and restorative grooming. With a verified 4.7-star reputation and a status as an essential cornerstone of the Bergen neighborhood, this facility delivers a high-touch and exceptionally professional care solution. Whether your companion is visiting for a signature coat styling or you are looking for expert nutritional advice, the team here treats every guest with the same expert heart and professional reliability.4d:T50b,Berry Lane Park Dog Run is a modern, vibrant highlight within [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj)'s largest municipal park. Revitalized from former industrial land into a green oasis, this dog run features a high-quality K9 synthetic turf surface, ensuring a mud-free experience that keeps paws clean and ready for the car ride home. The facility is fully fenced and equipped with essential amenities, including waste bag dispensers, trash receptacles, and benches for owners to relax while supervising play. Its integration into the wider Berry Lane Park means access to restrooms and other recreational zones nearby.\\n\\nThe dog run is known for its social atmosphere, often bustling with locals from the Bergen-Lafayette neighborhood. While it functions primarily as a single mixed-use run (without permanent separation for sizes in some configurations), the community is generally attentive and friendly. Lighting allows for safe use during early winter evenings. The park's convenient location near the Garfield Avenue Light Rail station makes it easily accessible. After a high-energy play session, owners often take a cooling leashed walk through the surrounding 17-acre park, which features rain gardens and over 600 newer trees, making it a complete outing for both pet and parent.4e:T7ef,Casa De Boop in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is an elite, high-touch pet care enclave that operates with a signature 'Mi Casa Su Casa' philosophy, providing a deeply restorative and personalized alternative to traditional boarding facilities. This facility-exclusive service is celebrated for its commitment to providing a 'sanctuary' environment, specializing in the expert care of shy rescues, senior dogs, and those with separation anxiety who require a quiet and authoritative presence. The hallmark of the Casa De Boop experience is its rare, downtown fenced yard—a world-class amenity in Jersey City—providing a secure and healthy space for fresh-air social sessions and spirited, supervised playtime. Led by a Red Cross certified professional in Pet First Aid and Canine CPR, the facility ensures that every guest is managed with the same expert logic and medical safety as a family companion.\n\nThe service menu at Casa De Boop is as personalized as it is professional, featuring a daily routine that includes bi-hourly potty breaks, frequent scenic neighborhood walks, and structured mental stimulation sessions. Unlike traditional kennels, the facility is a non-smoking, child-free, and pet-exclusive household where animals are allowed on all furniture and beds to maintain their home comfort levels. Owners benefit from total transparency, receiving frequent digital updates with high-quality photos and videos throughout their pet's stay. The team is particularly adept at professional medication administration and managing specialized geriatric routines, making it a vital and verified resource for the local community. With a perfect 5.0-star reputation and its status as a premier 'boutique' retreat, Casa De Boop delivers an exceptionally helpful and deeply affectionate care solution. Whether your companion is an active pup needing a secure yard to run or a senior socialite seeking a quiet afternoon on the couch, the team treats every guest with the elite care and personalized heart they deserve.4f:T7b2,Catch Air Jersey City in [Jersey City](/citi