 standard perk, keeping owners connected to their pet's adventures. By offering flexible playcare schedules and a cage-free, home-like boarding environment, Allforthewag appeals to discerning owners who want their dogs to feel loved and at home, rather than just housed, while they are away.\",\"slug\":\"allforthewag\",\"address\":\"205 15th St\",\"street\":\"205 15th St\",\"city\":\"Jersey City\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07310\",\"full_address\":\"205 15th St, Jersey City, NJ 07310, USA\",\"latitude\":40.73223949999999,\"longitude\":-74.0416939,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ60TcM2xvjIERrfWoM24ZEs0\",\"phone\":\"\",\"website\":\"http://www.allforthewag.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":146,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJbSC_mRxRwokRU3hrUcdRk1Q\",\"name\":\"Allforthewag Bergen Lafayette\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$49\",\"slug\":\"allforthewag-bergen-lafayette\",\"address\":\"333 Communipaw Ave\",\"street\":\"333 Communipaw Ave\",\"city\":\"Jersey City\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07304\",\"full_address\":\"333 Communipaw Ave, Jersey City, NJ 07304, USA\",\"latitude\":40.7105752,\"longitude\":-74.06186629999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJbSC_mRxRwokRU3hrUcdRk1Q\",\"phone\":\"(844) 484-3924\",\"website\":\"https://www.allforthewag.com/\",\"photo