sday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"6:00 AM – 10:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJy8syCThRwokRj4TmWX59pc8\",\"name\":\"Van Vorst Park Dog Run\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Located in the historic and picturesque Van Vorst Park neighborhood of [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), this dog run (often simply listed as 'Dog Park' on maps) is a cherished community hub. Known locally as the Van Vorst Park Dog Run, it offers a well-maintained, gravel-surfaced play area that fits perfectly into the elegant, brownstone-lined surroundings. The run provides a safe, fenced-in space for urban dogs to off-leash and socialize beneath the shade of mature trees.\\\\n\\\\nThe vibe here is distinctly neighborly; it's a place where regulars know each other by name (or by dog). Amenities include seating for owners and water availability to keep pets hydrated. Its central location makes it an ideal stop for a morning routine or an evening unwind. While the gravel surface helps keep mud at bay, it can be dusty, so casual attire is recommended. It is a vital green lung in the city where dogs can be dogs.\",\"slug\":\"dog-park\",\"address\":\"308 York St\",\"street\":\"308 York St\",\"city\":\"Jersey City\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07302\",\"full_address\":\"308 York St, Jersey City, NJ 07302, USA\",\"latitude\":40.7182901,\"longitude\":-74.0473597,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJy8syCTh