gorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://lepetitshampoodle.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.42:T816,Liberty Dog Walking & Pet Sitting in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a premier, dual-enterprise pet care solution that offers an exceptionally high level of personalized attention for the downtown community. Managed by certified professionals Alex and Stephanie, this service is celebrated for its 'pet-first' philosophy, specializing in premium dog daycare, professional walking, and specialized cat sitting services. The facility's hallmark is its absolute transparency, providing pet parents with constant photo and text updates, GPS-tracked walk journals, and tailored activity logs that ensure every companion's unique personality and energy level is scrupulously respected. Whether your pup requires a high-intensity 60-minute neighborhood hike or a restorative midday session of 'Puppy Walk and Play,' the team delivers a service that is both technically expert and deeply affectionate.\n\nThe service menu at Liberty is remarkably comprehensive, featuring unique amenities like a local pick-up and drop-off service for several residential towers, including Liberty Terrace and Portside. Their boarding program (available as '24-hour' or 'Extended' care) focuses on creating a home-away-from-home experience, replacing traditional kennels with a one-on-one environment optimized for enrichment, relaxation, and healthy socialization. For feline guests, the team provides specialized in-home care that includes expert medication administration, litter maintenance, and meaningful social interaction for even the most reclusive cats. Both owners are certified in Pet CPR and First Aid through the American Red Cross, reinforcing the facility's status as a verified and authoritative local resource. With a perfect 4.8-star reputation and a dedication to flexible, client-centric scheduling, Liberty Dog Walking delivers a world-class care solution. Whether you are seeking a reliable daily walker or a secure overnight haven for your companion, the team treats every guest with the same expert logic and individualized love that has made them a local legend.43:T807,Lighthouse Dog Run in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a premier waterfront destination that offers some of the most spectacular, panoramic views of the Manhattan skyline in the tri-state area. Located at Newport Tower Suites near the iconic LeFrak Point Lighthouse, this spacious and secure run provides an elite level of aesthetic beauty and functional play space for the Newport community. The facility features a professional-grade gravel surface that ensures proper drainage and a clean environment for dogs of all sizes to engage in vigorous social play. Its unique positioning along the Hudson River provides a refreshing waterfront breeze, making it one of the most comfortable and visually stunning spots for an early morning or sunset exercise session.\n\nThe amenities at Lighthouse Dog Run are focused on providing a restorative experience for both pets and their owners, featuring multiple benches strategically positioned to maximize the view while keeping a clear line of sight on the play area. The park's philosophy centers on creating a 'zen-like' social hub where urban dogs can burn off energy against a world-class architectural backdrop. Because of its proximity to the Newport PATH station and several luxury residential towers, the run maintains a sophisticated and respectful atmosphere, supported by a community of responsible pet owners who prioritize cleanliness and safety. While the run provides ample space for off-leash activities, its location within the larger Newport riverfront development also offers access to miles of leashed walking paths for those seeking a more quiet or technical stroll. With its verified reputation for safety and its status as a must-visit landmark for local photographers and pet parents alike, Lighthouse Dog Run delivers an authoritative and exceptionally picturesque care solution. Whether your pup is an urban explorer or just in need of a fresh-air social break, this Newport treasure treats every guest with the same expert logic and first-class views the community is famous for.44:T4cf,Part of the expansive Lincoln Park system in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), the Lincoln Park Dog Run offers a much-needed outlet for urban dogs to stretch their legs. The run features a cleaner, more modern artificial turf surface, which is a significant perk for owners looking to avoid the 'muddy paw' aftermath of natural grass parks. The facility is fully fenced and includes separate zones for small and large breeds, ensuring that play remains safe and balanced. Its location within one of Hudson County's largest parks means that a visit here is often just the beginning of a longer outdoor adventure.\\n\\nRegulars appreciate the reliable maintenance and the community vide, where neighbors catch up while their dogs wrestle on the turf. Benches and waste stations are standard amenities, and the run is well-lit for evening use, accommodating the schedule of the city's commuters. Finding the specific entrance can sometimes be tricky for first-timers—it sits near the athletic fields and wetland restoration areas—but the destination rewards the effort with a spacious, clean, and safe environment. Whether you're a local or visiting continuously improving Lincoln Park West, this dog run is a top-tier amenity.45:T76e,Lincoln Park Mini Dog Run in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a distinguished neighborhood enclave that serves as a quiet and restorative satellite to the massive regional Lincoln Park complex. Located near the Nunda Avenue corridor, this 'Mini' run is celebrated for its 'compact-but-complete' design, providing a secure and intimate social environment that is particularly valued by owners of smaller or more sensitive companions. The facility features a high-standard gravel surface engineered for transparency and drainage, ensuring a hygienic and low-dust play area regardless of the weather. Its double-gated entry system provides an elite measure of safety, allowing urban pet parents to handle their companions with expert logic and confidence during the transition from the city streets to the off-leash zone.\n\nThe service menu at the Lincoln Park Mini Run focuses on high-standard maintenance and essential pup hygiene, featuring authoritative amenities like a signature fire hydrant focus point, multiple waste stations, and shaded seating for restorative pet parent rest. The facility benefits from the world-class oversight of the Hudson County park system, ensuring regular social proofing and routine cleanup to maintain its verified 4.7-star reputation. While smaller in scale than its West Park Drive counterpart, this Nunda Avenue location offers a peaceful alternative for dogs who prefer a less overwhelming social environment. The park is surrounded by the lush landscaping of the broader Lincoln Park, providing easy access to miles of scenic walking trails and historic picnic groves after a spirited off-leash session. Whether your pup is visiting for a quick afternoon social break or a quiet morning of restorative play, this neighborhood landmark treats every guest with the same expert care and professional reliability found across the county’s elite park system.46:T821,Marin Green Dog Park in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a modern and exceptionally well-designed urban run that serves as a vital social centerpiece for the Hamilton Park and Marin Boulevard communities. Located adjacent to the 485 Marin residential complex, this spacious park is celebrated for its use of professional-grade, well-draining AstroTurf, which ensures a pristine and mud-free play surface even in wet conditions. The facility is intelligently organized into two distinct sections to separate larger and smaller dogs, providing a safe and controlled environment that encourages healthy social interaction for all sizes. Its 'city-garden' aesthetic combines lush greenery with a highly functional layout, making it a favorite destination for local pet parents seeking a serene but energetic park experience.\n\nThe amenities at Marin Green are thoughtfully curated for the modern pet owner, featuring multiple seating areas and shaded zones where residents can relax while monitoring their companions. To maintain its high standards of hygiene, the park provides ample waste stations and a dedicated clean-up infrastructure that reflects its status as a verified community-managed space. While the dog run provides a dedicated off-leash zone, the larger Marin Green urban park also offers a children's playground and beautifully maintained grassy lawns, allowing families to enjoy a multi-functional outdoor trip in one convenient location. Pet parents should note that while the park is a paradise for social play, they should bring their own water for their pups, as the run is designed to stay dry and clean. With its verified reputation forTechnical excellence and a staff-free management model that relies on responsible neighborhood stewardship, Marin Green Dog Park delivers an essential and authoritative outdoor solution. Whether your dog is seeking a high-energy game of chase on the turf or a quiet social break in the shade, this park treats every guest with the professional logic and community-oriented heart that defines the Jersey City lifestyle.47:T55d,Situated within the polished waterfront community of [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj)'s Newport neighborhood, the Newport Dog Park (often referred to as the Newport Dog Run) offers a pristine, modern play experience. The facility features a high-quality artificial turf surface that keeps dogs clean even after a vigorous romp, a major upgrade from the dust and mud common in older city runs. Divided into separate sections for large and small breeds, it ensures a safe environment for everyone from Great Danes to Chihuahuas. The run is fully fenced with well-maintained gates, giving owners peace of mind while their pets burn off energy.\\n\\nThe park's location is a standout feature, offering glimpses of the Manhattan skyline and sitting just steps away from the scenic Hudson River Waterfront Walkway. It is well-lit for evening visits, catering to the schedule of busy commuters utilizing the nearby PATH station. Benches are available for pet parents, along with on-site waste bag dispensers and trash receptacles to keep the area tidy. While technically a privately managed space for the Newport community, it serves as a central hub for local dog lovers who appreciate its cleanliness and 'resort-style' maintenance. Whether for a quick morning relief break or an evening social hour, it provides a crucial slice of open space in a high-density urban setting.48:T70e,Newport Pier Dog Run in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a spectacular waterfront destination that offers an elite urban exercise experience along the Hudson River. This world-class facility features professional-grade faux grass and a meticulously maintained, fully fenced layout designed to provide a secure and social environment for the local canine community. The park is celebrated for its breathtaking, unimpeded views of the Manhattan skyline, making every social session a visually restorative experience for pet parents. With its strategic location near the Newport Green urban beach and boardwalk, the run serves as an essential resource for residents who value a high-standard outdoor lifestyle and a scrupulously clean, well-lit space for their companions to play regardless of the hour.\n\nThe service menu at Newport Pier is remarkably comprehensive, featuring authoritative amenities like separate large and small dog sections, high-tech water stations to ensure pup hydration, and multiple shaded benches for restorative rest. The facility utilizes a high-standard hygiene protocol, providing complimentary waste bags and strategically placed trash bins to maintain the pristine quality of the faux turf. Beyond the fenced run, the surrounding Newport Green complex offers over four acres of world-class recreation, including a large 'catch' field, seasonal splash pads, and scenic walking trails along the riverfront. The facility is verified for its professional maintenance and secure, double-gated entry, providing an elite level of safety for urban pups. Whether your companion is a socially relaxed senior pup or an energetic urban explorer, Newport Pier treats every guest with the same expert logic and world-class beauty that defines this premier Hudson County neighborhood.49:T874,Palisades Pups in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a premier, 3,000-square-foot pet care complex that brings a sophisticated and multi-functional approach to animal wellness in the Heights. Located prominently on Central Avenue, this facility features a balanced layout of 1,800 square feet of climate-controlled indoor space and a dedicated 1,200-square-foot secure outdoor play area, ensuring that canine guests have ample room for both sheltered and fresh-air exercise. The facility's hallmark is its patient-first philosophy, particularly within its professional grooming department, which is renowned for using gentle, technical methods to ensure that even the most anxious or senior pets feel calm and secure. Their signature 'Cage-Free' drying process and individualized attention during bathing sessions eliminate the stress typically associated with traditional grooming environments, leaving pets refreshed and socially relaxed.\n\nThe service menu at Palisades Pups is remarkably comprehensive, offering everything from 13-hour supervised daycare sessions and professional dog walking to specialized cat grooming and in-home pet sitting services. For those seeking total convenience, the facility provides an authoritative 'Pet Taxi' transportation service, ensuring that your companion can reach their appointments safely and on time from anywhere in the city. Their boarding program is equally well-regarded, featuring a meticulous pre-boarding assessment that includes a free trial day and temperament test to guarantee a harmonious and safe social environment for all participants. The staff is verified for their expertise in handling diverse breeds and temperaments, offering regular digital report cards and health monitoring to provide pet parents with absolute peace of mind. With over 221 positive reviews and a status as a trusted community resource, Palisades Pups delivers a high-touch and exceptionally professional care solution. Whether your pup is coming in for a day of high-energy social play or a restorative grooming treatment, the team treats every guest with the elite logic and care that defines their professional mission.4a:T76e,Paws & Go in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj) is a premier mobile pet care destination that brings the world-class grooming experience of a high-end salon directly to your home or workplace. Operating out of a state-of-the-art, fully autonomous van equipped with dedicated climate control (both AC and heat), a professional-grade tub, and its own power generator, this service offers an elite level of convenience for busy urban families. The facility's hallmark is its cage-free, one-on-one philosophy, which provides a calm and restorative environment where every dog receives the stylist's undivided attention without the stress of travel or traditional salon noise. Their commitment to using natural, organic, and premium-grade products ensures that every session is as healthy as it is aesthetically restorative.\n\nThe service menu at Paws & Go is remarkably granular, offering signature multi-step treatments like the 'Basic Bath,' which includes a brightening natural blueberry facial and therapeutic coat conditioning. For those seeking more technical grooming, their 'Full Groom' package provides comprehensive and authoritative care, including breed-specific haircuts, technical de-shedding, and detailed paw pad and sanitary hygiene. The mobile unit is also equipped to handle specialized needs such as skunk treatments, medicated baths for skin relief, and professional dental hygiene, making it a vital 'one-stop' resource for pet parents on the go. To maintain total transparency and ease, the service features a sophisticated online booking system and a verified 5.0-star reputation for professional reliability. Whether your pup is an urban socialite in need of a refreshing blueberry facial or a senior pet seeking a quiet, door-side grooming session, the team at Paws & Go treats every guest with the same expert logic and first-class care that defines their professional mission.4b:T6c0,Paws & Tales Doggy Playgroup brings a dynamic and adventurous spirit to pet care in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), offering services that go far beyond the typical daycare experience. Located on Montgomery Street, this facility is designed to be an active playground for dogs, featuring obstacle courses and pools that turn an ordinary day into an exciting enrichment session. The philosophy here is all about engagement; dogs aren't just watched, they are entertained and challenged in ways that promote healthy socialization and mental acuity. One of the most beloved and convenient features of Paws & Tales is their 'Dog Bus' service—a dedicated shuttle that picks up your pup from home and drops them off tired and happy at the end of the day. This door-to-door service is a lifesaver for busy commuters and adds an element of school-bus fun to the dog's daily routine.\\n\\nThe staff at Paws & Tales are widely praised for their deep understanding of dog behavior and their genuine passion for animal welfare. They take the time to learn the unique personality