656-0959\",\"website\":\"http://www.palisadespups.net/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.4,\"reviewCount\":221,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJwZLJc2tXwokR4hWGCKmAcgE\",\"name\":\"Pawfessional Pet Care\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Jersey City](/cities/jersey-city-nj), look no further than Pawfessional Pet Care. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \\\"place to be\\\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 5-star rating from 3 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\\n\\nAt Pawfessional Pet Care, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Jersey City scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\",\"slug\":\"pawfessional-pet-care\",\"address\":\"371 Bergen Av